{"tid":2259463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內企「快手」 喺廁所裝計時器監控員工 網民：杜絕帶薪拉屎","createTime":"2020-10-27T00:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T04:56:35.000Z","uid":271829,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e5aa7be3709d6bb98677caa0d791e9dcdfb318ea","tid":2259463,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n內地短片App企業「快手」，管理層近日被員工投訴在洗手間安裝計時器，統計員工如廁時間，做法引發員工質疑，現在「連上廁所這種人類基本生理需求都不能滿足了」。然而，企業卻解釋是要統計洗手間使用次數，以判斷增加多少流動廁所，解決員工排隊上廁所問題。<br />\n<br />\n內地社交媒體近日流傳一篇文章「打工人，你是否為廁所拼（拚）過命？」，作者指快手在辦公室內洗手間加裝計時器。照片所見廁格上方確有計時器，會顯示該廁格是否有人使用，同時亦計算着員工如廁用了多少時間。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/ZMO42WZBUFCBJCS7EYXLR3CRWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2FZMO42WZBUFCBJCS7EYXLR3CRWQ%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=ed43845e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2FZMO42WZBUFCBJCS7EYXLR3CRWQ%2F&h=3a15ec06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/ZMO42WZBUFCBJCS7EYXLR3CRWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"75c1eca0718df149fa0ca9e1b1974064a651669f","tid":2259463,"uid":155732,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:30:09.000Z","msg":"真係名乎其實快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a48bdfb393f69b0c9c3d81d44632125cad32ff0","tid":2259463,"uid":218,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"點解唔學支那醫護著尿片返工？"},{"pid":"35763909436faf2cb0fbb8e79c69ad5450798e99","tid":2259463,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:56:54.000Z","msg":"要係位屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49c76f0a9e9f039deddd3381b40d2f2d0a8bf0e","tid":2259463,"uid":44171,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202